                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341124-18-offence-1 t18341124-cd-16"></join>21st of November</rs>, one handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18341124-name-180" type="victimName">
